    "17724946041ecbaa54": {
      "type": "_blocks",
      "blocks": {
        "ai_gen_block_27c36f2_7HcDgF": {
          "type": "ai_gen_block_27c36f2",
          "settings": {
            "desktop_width_percent": 100,
            "image_width": 70,
            "image_padding": 20,
            "content_padding": 40,
            "border_radius": 0,
            "background_color": "#666666",
            "heading_color": "#ffffff",
            "text_color": "#ffffff",
            "heading_size": 36,
            "text_size": 16,
            "button_size": 50,
            "button_offset": 20,
            "button_background": "#ffffff",
            "button_hover_background": "#f0f0f0",
            "button_color": "#1f1f21",
            "dot_color": "#ffffff",
            "slide_1_image": "shopify://shop_images/20240114__BE14.425.9_b064afa8-de2f-4b3b-889f-8e1186627eb5.png",
            "slide_1_heading": "RFN Warrior Pro SX-E15: The Gas Killer",
            "slide_1_text": "<p>Designed from the wheels up as a true motocross/trail bike, the E15 is competitive at the championship level of the 85cc class. Minimal maintenance - spend less time in the garage and more time riding!</p>",
            "slide_2_image": "shopify://shop_images/motor_bg_666666_fixed.png",
            "slide_2_heading": "Direct Drive Motor - First in Class",
            "slide_2_text": "<p>Powered by the world’s first direct-drive axial flux motor. By eliminating multi-stage gearing, more energy goes straight to the rear wheel — delivering more power and torque to the tire than competitors rated at the same output or even higher power outputs.</p>",
            "slide_3_image": "shopify://shop_images/RFN_26_MX_range_12.jpg",
            "slide_3_heading": "Fully Adjustable Suspension",
            "slide_3_text": "<p>Fully adjustable rebound and damping let you fine-tune the bike to your speed, terrain, and riding style. Whether you're on a smooth track boosting jumps or a gnarly rock garden, the forks and shock deliver consistent, predictable performance under load, improving corner stability, traction, and control when the pace picks up.</p>",
            "slide_4_image": "shopify://shop_images/RFN_26_MX_range_10.jpg",
            "slide_4_heading": "Unmatched Customization",
            "slide_4_text": "<p>Know exactly how your bike will ride. Five selectable power modes and 10+ fully adjustable in-app settings let you transform the ride from a full-power machine to a smooth, controlled learning platform. A reverse function makes tight maneuvering effortless without unnecessary fatigue, while the safety tether adds an extra layer of protection for both rider and surroundings. The LCD display keeps critical ride data front and center, so you’re always informed and in command.</p>",
            "slide_5_image": "shopify://shop_images/RFN_26_MX_range_23.jpg",
            "slide_5_heading": "Race-Worthy Brakes",
            "slide_5_text": "<p>With safety in mind, the SX-E15 is equipped with high-performance braking components built for steep descents and hard charging into corners. Strong initial bite and consistent stopping power deliver precise control on entry, while balanced modulation allows you to brake later with greater confidence through technical sections and high-speed terrain all while keeping the brakes from overheating.</p>",
            "slide_6_image": "shopify://shop_images/RFN_26_MX_range_64.jpg",
            "slide_6_heading": "Quick-Swap Battery",
            "slide_6_text": "<p>The fun never stops. Easily swap out the battery for a fresh pack in under 90 seconds - the same amount of time it takes to fill up a  tank without the hassle and danger of gas.</p>",
            "slide_7_image": "shopify://shop_images/frame_bg_666666.png",
            "slide_7_heading": "Precision Control",
            "slide_7_text": "<p>Industrly leading frame design & throttle control. The frame made of from aerospace-grade aluminum is more responsive under load. With the with advanced real-time control architecture the SX-E15 crafts smoother acceleration, cleaner drive out of corners, and controlled traction in technical terrain and on whoops.</p>"
          },
          "blocks": {}
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "ai_gen_block_27c36f2_7HcDgF"
      ],
      "settings": {}
